        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/j/3d9bf3/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2018-10-31T17:17:48.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I\u2019ve had a very nice 1993 Noellat from boudots\u2013don\u2019t have my notes at the moment, but I think it was Charles.  It was actually one of the top bottles in a horizontal about 3 years ago that included most major producers.  I would be a little nervous about an 86, but don\u2019t have any experience to report.</p>",
