        "created_at": "2018-11-01T09:09:47.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"8\" data-topic=\"146934\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>Oops\u2013sorry\u2013I was thinking Georges Noellat and typed Charles.  It was the 93 Georges Noellat\u2013the horizontal was in 2011.  Also had the Leroy that night (so in effect sort of had the Charles).  I found a couple more bottles of the 93 Georges N. Boudots, last consumed in 2017, all consistently very good.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Sounds great. The 1993 Leroys are extremely rare (and expensive) due to the very low yields \u2026<br>\nNever had a 1993 George Noellat \u2026</p>",
